Enhances: markdown
Description: Markdown editor with AI assistant
 A modern, open-source Markdown editor licensed under the MIT License.
 .
 Built with Python and PySide6, it combines a cozy, efficient UI with powerful
 tools and an integrated AI assistant. Notolog is designed to help developers
 and writers focus, prototype ideas, and sharpen their Markdown fluency.
 .
 For more information, see the Notolog website.
